question: Ashley is required to submit a 36-page dissertation. She already finished writing 1/6 of the dissertation. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Ashley has already written 1/6 of the dissertation which is 36 pages*1/6 = <<36*1/6=6>>6 pages.
So, she still needs to write 36 pages - 6 pages = <<36-6=30>>30 pages.
#### 30
